channel.title: Need help with looking and researching sources
channel.description: Hey guys! Soooo I'm finally wanting to get back to try and learning how to "code" a server, and to kind of narrow it down I'm looking for a 317 or Pi that doesn't have any customs or dumbass stuff. I'm basically just wanting a "cleaned" source but not totally cleaned (file wise). I am a beginner so if anyone has a source and client they started with please feel free to share with me! And I know what you're gonna say, "did you check google?, did you check rune-server?, Did you check moparscape server downloads? And the answer is YES. And neither of those sites have what I'm looking for. I know someone out there could be some assistance. Please let me know!
